Class AverageRatingDetailsType

java.lang.Object
  com.ebay.soap.eBLBaseComponents.AverageRatingDetailsType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AverageRatingDetailsType
extends Object
implements Serializable

Applicable to sites that support the Detailed Seller Ratings feature. The AverageRatingDetailsType container consists of the average detailed seller ratings in an area. When buyers leave an overall Feedback rating (positive, neutral, or negative) for a seller, they also can leave ratings in four areas: item as described, communication, shipping time, and charges for shipping and handling. Users retrieve detailed ratings as averages of the ratings left by buyers.
